## TagTales Gallery
Piattaforma graffiti: mostre, writers, magazine, shop Ecwid. Lingua primaria IT. Dettaglio prodotto: @PRD.md @SPEC.md @ROADMAP.md

## Stack
React 19 + Vite + TypeScript + Tailwind | Express in `server.ts` → `dist/server.js` | Firebase Auth/Firestore/Storage

## Comandi
- `npm run dev` — localhost:3000
- `npm run lint` — typecheck
- `npm test` — Vitest
- `npm run build` / `npm start` — produzione

